<!-- ==================== 考試公式速查表 ==================== -->
<section id="cheatsheet">
<h1>📋 考試公式速查表</h1>
<div class="formula">═══════════════════════════════════════
         考試公式速查表
═══════════════════════════════════════

【Probability Distribution】
ΣP = 1
E(X) = Σ x·P(X=x)
Var(X) = E(X²) − [E(X)]²
SD = √Var

【Linear Transformation Y = aX + b】
E(Y) = aE(X) + b
Var(Y) = a²·Var(X)     ← b 唔影響！
SD(Y) = |a|·SD(X)

【Independent: T = X + Y】
E(T) = E(X) + E(Y)
Var(T) = Var(X) + Var(Y)
SD(T) = √[Var(X)+Var(Y)]  ← SD 唔可以直接加！

【Normal Distribution】
Z = (X − μ) / σ
P(Z &lt; −a) = 0.5 − P(0&lt;Z&lt;a)
反查：M = μ + Zσ

【Confidence Interval】
σ known:  x̄ ± Z × σ/√n
σ unknown: x̄ ± t × s/√n  (df=n−1)
Proportion: p̂ ± Z × √[p̂(1−p̂)/n]
Min n = (Zσ/ME)² → ROUND UP!

Z values: 90%→1.645  95%→1.96  98%→2.326  99%→2.576

【Price Index】
Laspeyres = Σq₀pₜ / Σq₀p₀ × 100  (L=舊q)
Paasche = Σqₜpₜ / Σqₜp₀ × 100    (P=新q)

【CPI】
Inflation Rate = (CPI_new − CPI_old)/CPI_old × 100%

【Descriptive Stats】
Mean = Σx/n
SD = √[(Σx²−nx̄²)/(n−1)]
Q₁位置 = ¼(n+1), Q₃位置 = ¾(n+1)
Skew: Q₃−Q₂ > Q₂−Q₁ → Positive

【Time Series】
SV = Original − Moving Average
═══════════════════════════════════════</div>

