<section id="q1">
<h1>📘 Q1：Sampling Methods（抽樣方法）</h1>

<h3>🔍 咩係 Sampling（抽樣）？</h3>
<p>你唔可能問全世界每一個人嘅意見，所以你揀一部分人嚟代表成個群體，呢個過程就叫 <strong>Sampling</strong>。</p>

<h3>📌 三種必識嘅 Sampling Methods：</h3>

<h4>1️⃣ Simple Random Sampling（簡單隨機抽樣）</h4>
<ul>
<li><strong>Definition</strong>: Every member of the population has an <strong>equal chance</strong> of being selected.</li>
<li><strong>白話</strong>：好似抽獎咁，每個人被抽中嘅機會一樣。</li>
<li><strong>例子</strong>：Q1(a)(i) — 從所有註冊醫生入面隨機揀 50 個做調查。</li>
</ul>

<h4>2️⃣ Stratified Sampling（分層抽樣）</h4>
<ul>
<li><strong>Definition</strong>: Population divided into <strong>subgroups (strata)</strong>, then random samples drawn from <strong>each stratum</strong>.</li>
<li><strong>白話</strong>：先分組（例如按部門），再喺每組入面各自隨機抽人。</li>
<li><strong>例子</strong>：Q1(a)(ii) — 銀行有 Marketing、Research、Finance 三個部門，分別隨機抽 30、20、50 人。</li>
</ul>

<h4>3️⃣ Systematic Sampling（系統抽樣）</h4>
<ul>
<li><strong>Definition</strong>: Select every <strong>k-th</strong> member from a list or sequence.</li>
<li><strong>白話</strong>：每隔固定人數抽一個。</li>
<li><strong>例子</strong>：Q1(a)(iii) — 每第 8 個入學校嘅學生就問佢最鍾意邊個老師。</li>
</ul>

<h3>✅ Q1(a) 答案：</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>情境</th><th>答案</th></tr>
<tr><td>(i) 隨機揀 50 個醫生</td><td><strong>Simple Random Sampling</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>(ii) 按部門各自抽人</td><td><strong>Stratified Sampling</strong></td></tr>
<tr><td>(iii) 每第 8 個學生</td><td><strong>Systematic Sampling</strong></td></tr>
</table>

<div class="box-tip">
<p>🧠 <strong>考試 Tips</strong>：</p>
<ul>
<li>見到 "randomly selected from the whole group" → Simple Random</li>
<li>見到 "divided into groups / departments" → Stratified</li>
<li>見到 "every k-th" → Systematic</li>
</ul>
</div>
</section>

<!-- ==================== Q2 ==================== -->
<section id="q2">
<h1>📘 Q2：Normal Distribution 常態分佈綜合題</h1>
<p><strong>題目背景</strong>：ABC 航空公司由香港飛台灣嘅飛行時間 X ~ N(90, 15²)</p>

<h3>🔑 Z-Score（標準分數）</h3>
<div class="formula">Z = (X − μ) / σ</div>
<p>Z 嘅意思：呢個數值距離 mean 有幾多個 standard deviation</p>

<h3>📊 Normal Table 點用？</h3>
<ul>
<li>呢份卷嘅 Table：P(0 &lt; Z &lt; z) = 由 0 到 z 之間嘅面積</li>
<li>成條鐘形曲線嘅<strong>總面積 = 1</strong>，左半邊 = 0.5，右半邊 = 0.5</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h3>Q2(a)：P(X &lt; 81) = ?</h3>
<div class="step">
<p><strong>Step 1</strong>：Z = (81 − 90) / 15 = −0.6</p>
<p><strong>Step 2</strong>：P(Z &lt; −0.6) = 0.5 − P(0 &lt; Z &lt; 0.6)</p>
<p><strong>Step 3</strong>：查表 P(0&lt;Z&lt;0.6) = 0.2257</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">P(X &lt; 81) = 0.5 − 0.2257 = <strong>0.2743</strong></div>

<hr>

<h3>Q2(b)：搵 M，使得 P(X &gt; M) = 0.20</h3>
<div class="step">
<p><strong>Step 1</strong>：P(X &gt; M) = 0.20 → P(X &lt; M) = 0.80 → P(0&lt;Z&lt;z) = 0.30</p>
<p><strong>Step 2</strong>：反查表 → Z ≈ 0.84</p>
<p><strong>Step 3</strong>：M = 90 + 0.84 × 15 = 90 + 12.6</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">M = <strong>102.6 minutes</strong></div>

<hr>

<h3>Q2(c)：Binomial Distribution 題</h3>
<p>隨機抽 20 班機，求剛好 5 班飛行時間少過 81 分鐘嘅概率</p>
<div class="step">
<p>由 part (a)：p = P(X &lt; 81) = 0.2743</p>
<p>Y ~ Bin(n = 20, p = 0.2743)</p>
<p>P(Y = 5) = C(20,5) × (0.2743)⁵ × (0.7257)¹⁵</p>
<p>= 15504 × 0.001553 × 0.01026</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">P(Y = 5) ≈ <strong>0.2470</strong></div>

<div class="box-key">
<p><strong>Binomial 嘅條件</strong>：① 固定次數 n ② 每次只有兩個結果 ③ 每次概率 p 相同 ④ 各次獨立</p>
</div>

<hr>

<h3>Q2(d)：Linear Transformation</h3>
<p>升級後飛行時間減少 8%，新時間 = 0.92X</p>
<div class="answer">
<p>(i) E(0.92X) = 0.92 × 90 = <strong>82.8 minutes</strong></p>
<p>(ii) SD(0.92X) = 0.92 × 15 = <strong>13.8 minutes</strong></p>
</div>

<h3>📝 Q2 總結：</h3>
<table>
<tr><th>Part</th><th>考點</th><th>核心公式</th></tr>
<tr><td>(a)</td><td>Normal → Z-score → 查表</td><td>Z = (X − μ) / σ</td></tr>
<tr><td>(b)</td><td>反查 Normal Table</td><td>由概率搵 Z → X = μ + Zσ</td></tr>
<tr><td>(c)</td><td>Normal + Binomial 結合</td><td>用 (a) 嘅概率做 Binomial 嘅 p</td></tr>
<tr><td>(d)</td><td>Linear Transformation</td><td>E(aX) = aE(X), SD(aX) = |a|SD(X)</td></tr>
</table>
</section>

