<section id="q11">
<h1>📘 Q11：Confidence Interval 進階版</h1>
<p><strong>題目</strong>：ATM 交易時間 ~ Normal, σ = 0.4 (known!), n=25, x̄=2.2</p>

<h3>⚡ 關鍵判斷：σ = 0.4 已知 → 用 Z！</h3>

<h3>Q11(ai)：95% CI for Mean（σ known → Z）</h3>
<div class="step">
<p>Z₀.₀₂₅ = 1.96, SE = 0.4/√25 = 0.08</p>
<p>ME = 1.96 × 0.08 = 0.1568</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">95% CI = 2.2 ± 0.1568 = <strong>(2.0432, 2.3568) minutes</strong></div>

<h3>Q11(aii)：Minimum Sample Size（ME ≤ 0.08）</h3>
<div class="formula">n = (Z × σ / ME)² = (1.96 × 0.4 / 0.08)² = (9.8)² = 96.04</div>
<div class="answer">n = 96.04 → <strong>Round Up → n = 97</strong></div>
<div class="box-warn">
<p>⚠️ <strong>一定要 Round Up！</strong>96.04 → 97，唔係 96！</p>
</div>

<h3>Q11(b)：98% CI for Proportion</h3>
<p>n=300, 45 人提取超過 $1900, p̂ = 45/300 = 0.15</p>
<div class="step">
<p>Z₀.₀₁ = <strong>2.326</strong>（98% CI）</p>
<p>SE = √[0.15 × 0.85 / 300] = 0.02062</p>
<p>ME = 2.326 × 0.02062 = 0.04796</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">98% CI = 0.15 ± 0.04796 = <strong>(0.1020, 0.1980)</strong> 即 (10.20%, 19.80%)</div>
</section>

