<section id="q14">
<h1>📘 Q14：Normal Distribution 進階版 — 兩個獨立隨機變量</h1>
<p><strong>Tin Restaurant</strong>：X ~ N(160, 8²)</p>
<p><strong>Sam Steak House</strong>：Y ~ N(164, 15²)，X 同 Y 獨立</p>

<h3>Q14(a)：P(140 &lt; X &lt; 170)</h3>
<div class="step">
<p>Z₁ = (140−160)/8 = −2.5，Z₂ = (170−160)/8 = 1.25</p>
<p>P(−2.5 &lt; Z &lt; 1.25) = P(0&lt;Z&lt;2.5) + P(0&lt;Z&lt;1.25) = 0.4938 + 0.3944</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">P = <strong>0.8882</strong> (88.82%)</div>

<h3>Q14(b)：P(X ≥ M) = 0.80，搵 M</h3>
<div class="step">
<p>P(X &lt; M) = 0.20 → M 喺左邊 → Z = −0.84</p>
<p>M = 160 + (−0.84) × 8 = 160 − 6.72</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">M = <strong>153.28 thousand dollars</strong></div>

<h3>Q14(c)：T = X + Y</h3>
<div class="answer">
<p>(i) E(T) = 160 + 164 = <strong>324</strong></p>
<p>(ii) Var(T) = 8² + 15² = 64 + 225 = <strong>289</strong></p>
<p>(iii) SD(T) = √289 = <strong>17</strong></p>
<p>(iv) Median = <strong>324</strong>（Normal Distribution → Mean = Median）</p>
</div>
<div class="box-warn">
<p>⚠️ SD 唔可以直接加！❌ 8+15=23 | ✅ √(64+225) = √289 = 17</p>
</div>

<h3>Q14(d)：P(T &gt; 350) 高唔高？</h3>
<div class="step">
<p>T ~ N(324, 17²)</p>
<p>Z = (350−324)/17 = 26/17 ≈ 1.53</p>
<p>P(T &gt; 350) = 0.5 − P(0&lt;Z&lt;1.53) = 0.5 − 0.4370</p>
</div>
<div class="answer">P(T &gt; 350) = <strong>0.0630 (6.30%)</strong> → <strong>唔高！Samson 嘅講法唔啱。</strong></div>
<blockquote>"The probability is only 6.30%, which is very low. Therefore, it is NOT a high chance."</blockquote>
</section>

